    "h1_count": 1,
    "blockquote": "Frigade is an AI agent that learns your product by actually using it, then guides your users through real workflows inside your app. Unlike tools that rely on help docs or pre-built flows, Frigade autonomously navigates your product to understand how features connect, where users get stuck, and how to walk them through tasks step-by-step. It handles onboarding, in-app support, feature adoption, and user research in one platform.",
